    javax.security.auth.spi.LoginModule

    public class RptLoginModule
extends java.lang.Object
implements javax.security.auth.spi.LoginModule
    RptLoginModule is a LoginModule to authenticate user via the internal report. It is assumed that the MD5 ecrypted password is stored in a report.
